---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import desktopGallery from '../assets/Desktop1.png';
import mobileShare from '../assets/mobileShare2.png';
---

<!-- Hero Section - Full Viewport Height -->
<section class="relative overflow-hidden" style="height: calc(100vh - 4rem);">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-sky-500/5 via-blue-500/5 to-purple-500/5 dark:from-sky-500/10 dark:via-blue-500/10 dark:to-purple-500/10"></div>
  <div class="absolute inset-0">
    <div class="absolute top-20 left-10 w-72 h-72 bg-sky-200/20 dark:bg-sky-400/10 rounded-full blur-3xl animate-pulse"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-20 right-10 w-96 h-96 bg-purple-200/20 dark:bg-purple-400/10 rounded-full blur-3xl animate-pulse"></div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center flex flex-col justify-center items-center h-full">
    <div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-slate-900 dark:text-white leading-tight">
        Share Event Photos in 
        <span class="relative">
          <span class="block bg-gradient-to-r from-sky-600 via-blue-600 to-purple-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent">Seconds.</span>
          <div class="absolute -inset-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-sky-600/20 via-blue-600/20 to-purple-600/20 blur-lg -z-10"></div>
        </span>
        <span class="block text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl mt-2">Delight Every Guest.</span>
      </h1>
    </div>
    
    <div>
      <p class="mt-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto text-xl text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
        No zip files. No email threads. No compression. Create a temporary, private photo-sharing page—guests scan a QR code and download originals in seconds.
        <span class="font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200">No accounts, no hassle.</span>
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4">
      <a href="/sessions" class="group bg-gradient-to-r from-sky-600 to-blue-600 text-white font-semibold py-4 px-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-sky-500/25">
        <span class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
          Get Started
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10.293 3.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l6 6a1 1 0 010 1.414l-6 6a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L14.586 11H3a1 1 0 110-2h11.586l-4.293-4.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
          </svg>
        </span>
      </a>
      <a href="#how-it-works" class="backdrop-blur-sm bg-white/70 dark:bg-slate-800/70 text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 font-semibold py-4 px-8 rounded-xl hover:bg-white/80 dark:hover:bg-slate-800/80 transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 border border-white/50 dark:border-slate-700/50">
        How It Works
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Problems Section - Full Width -->
<section class="py-20 sm:py-24">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
        The Post-Event Photo Struggle is 
        <span class="text-red-600 dark:text-red-400">Real</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 mb-4">
        You've captured amazing moments. Now comes the part everyone dreads.
      </p>
      <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-red-500 to-orange-500 mx-auto rounded-full"></div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="mt-16 max-w-4xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <div class="group bg-white dark:bg-slate-900/80 p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300 border border-slate-200/50 dark:border-slate-800/50">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 h-12 w-12 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-red-500 to-pink-500 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
            <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M18.364 18.364A9 9 0 005.636 5.636m12.728 12.728L5.636 5.636m12.728 12.728L18.364 5.636M5.636 18.364l12.728-12.728"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Account Creation Headaches</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Force guests to create accounts just to see photos? It's a major barrier and frustration for them—and for you when trying to move your own.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="group bg-white dark:bg-slate-900/80 p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300 border border-slate-200/50 dark:border-slate-800/50">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 h-12 w-12 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-500 to-red-500 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
            <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 7v10a2 2 0 002 2h14a2 2 0 002-2V9a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2-2z"></path>
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8 7V5a2 2 0 012-2h4a2 2 0 012 2v2m-6 4l2 2 4-4"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2">The "Zip File Mess"</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Guests struggle with unzipping files on their phones, leading to endless support texts and confusion. You might even find yourself doing it.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="group bg-white dark:bg-slate-900/80 p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300 border border-slate-200/50 dark:border-slate-800/50">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 h-12 w-12 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-yellow-500 to-orange-500 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
            <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Loss of Quality</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Texts and social media apps compress your beautiful photos, diminishing their quality for everyone, including your personal archives.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="group bg-white dark:bg-slate-900/80 p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300 border border-slate-200/50 dark:border-slate-800/50">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 h-12 w-12 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500 to-pink-500 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
            <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Lingering Privacy Worries</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Permanent online galleries can feel exposed, and remembering to delete them is another chore, even for your own temporary sharing needs.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- How It Works Section - Full Width with Background -->
<section id="how-it-works" class="py-20 sm:py-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 via-blue-50/30 to-purple-50/30 dark:from-slate-900/50 dark:via-slate-900/80 dark:to-slate-900/50">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
        Simple, Private,
        <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-sky-600 to-purple-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent">Built for the Moment</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 mb-4">
        EversPass is designed for speed and simplicity, both for you and your guests.
      </p>
      <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-sky-500 to-purple-500 mx-auto rounded-full"></div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="mt-16 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-10">
        <!-- Step 1 -->
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="mx-auto h-16 w-16 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-sky-500 to-blue-600 flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg">
            <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">1</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mt-6 text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Upload Your Photos</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Add photos from any device—phone, tablet, or computer. Multiple people can contribute to the same session.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 2 -->
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="mx-auto h-16 w-16 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-purple-600 flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg">
            <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">2</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mt-6 text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Share the QR or Link</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Guests scan a code or tap a link—no app download, no sign-up. Works instantly across iOS, Android, and desktop.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 3 -->
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="mx-auto h-16 w-16 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500 to-pink-600 flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg">
            <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">3</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mt-6 text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Everyone Downloads & Keeps</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Guests pick their favorites and save originals in full quality. The session auto-deletes after 24 hours—nothing to clean up.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature pills -->
      <div class="mt-12 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900/70 px-4 py-2 rounded-full shadow-sm border border-slate-200/50 dark:border-slate-800/50 text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-sky-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
          </svg>
          Auto-deletes in 24 hours
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900/70 px-4 py-2 rounded-full shadow-sm border border-slate-200/50 dark:border-slate-800/50 text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-purple-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path>
          </svg>
          Multi-person uploads
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900/70 px-4 py-2 rounded-full shadow-sm border border-slate-200/50 dark:border-slate-800/50 text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-emerald-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4 16l4.586-4.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L16 16m-2-2l1.586-1.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L20 14m-6-6h.01M6 20h12a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
          </svg>
          Original quality preserved
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900/70 px-4 py-2 rounded-full shadow-sm border border-slate-200/50 dark:border-slate-800/50 text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-orange-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8 7H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v9a2 2 0 002 2h14a2 2 0 002-2V9a2 2 0 00-2-2h-3m-1 4l-3-3m0 0l-3 3m3-3v12"></path>
          </svg>
          PC to phone transfers
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Product Preview Section -->
<section class="py-20 sm:py-24">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
        What Your Guests See
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">
        A polished gallery that works on any device—no instructions needed.
      </p>
      <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-sky-500 to-purple-500 mx-auto rounded-full mt-4"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Desktop: layered mockup. Mobile: phone screenshot only. -->
    <div class="relative md:pb-28">
      <!-- Desktop screenshot — hidden on mobile -->
      <div class="hidden md:block rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl ring-1 ring-slate-900/10 dark:ring-white/10">
        <Image
          src={desktopGallery}
          alt="EversPass photo gallery on desktop"
          loading="lazy"
          class="w-full"
        />
      </div>

      <!-- Phone screenshot: overlay (desktop) or standalone (mobile) -->
      <div class="mx-auto w-52 md:absolute md:bottom-0 md:right-12 md:w-60 rounded-[2.5rem] overflow-hidden shadow-2xl ring-4 ring-white dark:ring-slate-900">
        <Image
          src={mobileShare}
          alt="EversPass share page with QR code on mobile"
          loading="lazy"
          class="w-full"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA Section - Full Width with Gradient Background -->
<section id="get-started" class="relative py-20 sm:py-24 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-400 via-purple-500 to-pink-500 dark:from-sky-600 dark:via-blue-600 dark:to-purple-700"></div>
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-20" style="background-image: url('data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width=&quot;60&quot; height=&quot;60&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 60 60&quot; xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&quot;%3E%3Cg fill=&quot;none&quot; fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot;%3E%3Cg fill=&quot;%23ffffff&quot; fill-opacity=&quot;0.1&quot;%3E%3Ccircle cx=&quot;30&quot; cy=&quot;30&quot; r=&quot;2&quot;/%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/svg%3E')"></div>
  
  <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
    <div>
      <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white mb-6">
        Ready to Simplify Your Photo Sharing?
      </h2>
      <p class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-xl text-blue-50 dark:text-blue-100 mb-10 leading-relaxed">
        Create a session in seconds, share a link, and let everyone grab their photos.
        <span class="font-semibold text-white">No setup. No sign-up. Just works.</span>
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div>
      <a href="/sessions" class="group inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-white text-blue-600 font-bold py-4 px-10 rounded-xl shadow-2xl hover:shadow-3xl transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300">
        <span class="text-lg">Try It Now</span>
        <svg class="w-6 h-6 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
          <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10.293 3.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l6 6a1 1 0 010 1.414l-6 6a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L14.586 11H3a1 1 0 110-2h11.586l-4.293-4.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
    
    <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap justify-center items-center gap-6 text-blue-100 dark:text-blue-200 text-sm">
      <span class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 10h18M7 15h1m4 0h1m-7 4h12a3 3 0 003-3V8a3 3 0 00-3-3H6a3 3 0 00-3 3v8a3 3 0 003 3z"></path>
        </svg>
        No credit card required
      </span>
      <span class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z"></path>
        </svg>
        Privacy-first
      </span>
      <span class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
        </svg>
        Works instantly
      </span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>